RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO, B.SHORT_NAME FROM OLVWS_PRODUCT_CUSTOMERS A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE =sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND A.CUSTOMER_NO = B.CUSTOMER_NO AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT B.BANK FROM LBTBS_ASSGN_VAL_BANKS B WHERE B.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND B.VERSION_NO = ? AND B.BANK_TYPE = 'ISSUING' AND B.BANK = A.CUSTOMER_NO) ORDER BY A.CUSTOMER_NO

SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO, USER_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT WHERE AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A' AND MODULE_CODE = 'LB' AND PRODUCT_TYPE = 'C' AND CONTRACT_REF_NO NOT IN (SELECT OTHER_TRANCHE_REF_NO FROM LBTBS_ASSGN_VAL_OTHER_TRANCHES WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO =? AND VERSION_NO = ? AND TRANCHE_TYPE = 'SIMULTANEOUS_TRANSFER') ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO

SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO , B.SHORT_NAME FROM OLVWS_PRODUCT_CUSTOMERS A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND A.CUSTOMER_NO = B.CUSTOMER_NO AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT B.BANK FROM LBTBS_ASSGN_VAL_BANKS B WHERE B.CONTRACT_REF_NO =? AND B.VERSION_NO = ? AND B.BANK_TYPE = 'SWINGLINE' AND B.BANK = A.CUSTOMER_NO)ORDER BY A.CUSTOMER_NO

SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO, USER_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT WHERE AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A' AND MODULE_CODE = 'LB' AND PRODUCT_TYPE = 'C' AND CONTRACT_REF_NO NOT IN (SELECT OTHER_TRANCHE_REF_NO FROM LBTBS_ASSGN_VAL_OTHER_TRANCHES WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO =? AND VERSION_NO =? AND TRANCHE_TYPE = 'OTHER') ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO
